<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OSHI TIME</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/app.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">

</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>OSHI TIME</h1>
        
        <p>Oshi Time is free-for-all application which aspires to be one stop solution for Businesses to keep track of their part-time employees worktime. 
            With this, Oshi Time is radically digitizing paper Payslip in Japan as, Businesses using Oshi Time are able to provide their part-time employees with streaming Payslip. 
        </p>
        <p>As our next project is under development, we are pleased to announce 
            our second product of Oshi ecosystem that will be salary live streaming application which will provide part-time employees instant access to their salary.  </p>
    </header> 
    <main>
    <section class="row boxes">
            <aside class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="container-box">
                    <div class="heading">
                        <h2>For Business</h2>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="detail-info">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Allows Business to track employees worktime</li>
                            <li>Oshi Time is free for all</li>
                            <li>Save money on other tracking software</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="link-button">
                        <form action="/firm/register">
                            <button class="black-button">Register</button>
                            <small>Already have an Account? Click below..</small>
                            <button class="blue-button" formaction="/firm/login">Log In</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>
            <aside class="col-sm-4">
                <div class="container-box">
                    <div class="heading">
                        <h2>For Employee</h2>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="detail-info">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Generates & Live Streams everyday earnings</li>
                            <li>Immediate access to salary fund on Oshi Wallet(soon available on next update)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="link-button">
                        <form action="/user/register">
                            <button class="black-button">Register</button>
                            <small>Already have an Account? Click below..</small>
                            <button class="blue-button" formaction="/user/login">Log In</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>
